title: Discussion about 23 kda + 100% winrate on twitch jungle KILLERTOAST949
body:
Anyone have any idea what is happening here with this guy?

Who is he?

Why is he averaging like a 99% winrate on anyone he is trying to win with and 0% winrate on champs he is trying to lose with?

https://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=KILLERTOAST949

Some google searches refer to imaqtpie. Can anyone confirm that he takes trips down to australia and then apparently plays twitch with a lolskillscore 1k above anyone else (including challenger)?

Can anyone find me or have a replay of this guys games?

replies.body: KILLERTOAST949 is the name of the url in imaqtpie's youtube channel.
right, but anyone could just create an account with that name, that is why I want to see this guy play from a replay, because his games seem to be too consistently lucky to be legitimate.

I was able to achieve his cs rate through jungle by farming non stop as quick as possible with unlimited health and mana (8 cs per min).

I was ALMOST able to achieve his gold at a set time (20 mins) by adding 10k gold in the training tool... he still had more.

Now this is my account which plays 5v5 flex with a whole team designed to keep me alive and funnel as much gold as possible into me.

https://oce.op.gg/summoner/userName=transcender
